    "Considerations": [
        "During system or software updates, legitimate modifications to the registry may occur, including changes to the Local Port Monitor settings. These updates can trigger alerts even though they are benign.",
        "When installing or updating printer drivers, the registry keys related to the Local Port Monitor may be modified. This is a common and expected behavior, which can lead to false positive alerts.",
